The '''Pyrolisk''', also known as '''Perilisk''' in the [[Nintendo Entertainment System]] version, is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]'' found in [[Mount Gulg (Final Fantasy)|Mount Gulg]], and in the [[Mirage Tower]]. It is an easy monster in the Mirage Tower, because the [[party]] is more [[Level|leveled up]] by this point. In the [[Waterfall Cavern]], on the south part of this cave, there is a room with many [[Treasure chest (object)|chests]] and a robot; a group of Pyrolisks, Cockatrices, and [[Mummy (Final Fantasy)|Mummies]] guard the room.

While a frail foe, the Pyrolisk should nonetheless be dealt with quickly, as it can try to instantly kill a party member through its [[Gaze (Final Fantasy)|Gaze]] attack. [[Blizzara (Final Fantasy)|Blizzara]] can make short work of a group of Pyrolisks, and can be cast for free using the [[Black Robe (Final Fantasy)|Black Robe]].

